{"tid":1625554,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[5 OCT] 機場快綫以外其他鐵路綫包括輕鐵今日全日暫停","createTime":"2019-10-05T07:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T07:38:09.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c57ec8c748dfa9dbaa8e88cb9b4c0769f676633b","tid":1625554,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:20:33.000Z","msg":"港鐵宣布，機場快綫列車服務以外，其他鐵路綫包括輕鐵今日全日暫停。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，多個港鐵車站早前遭受嚴重破壞，港鐵正努力修復。<br />\n<br />\n經與警方及相關政府部門進行風險評估後，機場快綫列車服務下午2時30分起恢復，因應機管局及政府要求，香港站至機場站來回方向維持10分鐘一班。而九龍站、青衣站及博覽館站則維持關閉。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵巴士將於下午4時起恢復有限度服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484440-20191005.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484440-20191005.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=6f5c5457\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484440-20191005.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3bf3190a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484440-20191005.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d34e1be452835f9daeac66f922e28bba3f83ea6b","tid":1625554,"uid":9570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:32:55.000Z","msg":"核爆都要開返個香港站，留意吓佢點封鐵香港站都盡量keep 住開"},{"pid":"954fc387689cd980d09e3a104e1dec7675d81072","tid":1625554,"uid":327169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:38:09.000Z","msg":"春袋<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}